        Create an answer with all the attributes (null possible)
        Parameters:
        id - The answer id
        creationDate - the date when the answer has been created
        deletionDate - the date when the answer has been deleted, null if the answer hasn't been deleted
        score - The answer score on SO
        body - The answer body
        lastEditDate - The last time the question has been edited
        closedDate - The date when the answer has been closed (null if the answer is open)
        communityOwnedDate - The date when the answer started to belong to the community
        owner - The user that owns the answer
        lastEditor - The last editor of the answer
        parentId - The parent id, i.e the question answered
